Package cz.cvut.fel.omo.model.house

Class House

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.omo.model.house.House
public class House extends Object

This class describes our House. This class includes all devices, floor, residents(pets, humans), transport. And this class implements Design Pattern Singleton
